  - 
  - '    '
  - You're just an unexpected guest inside someones mind. Enjoy the journey and watch
    the story unfold.
  - A silent world.
  - A world where things just stopped.
  - Not because of some cataclysm.
  - Not because of abandonment.
  - But because of the damage.
  - Damage dealt by others
  - things not considered properly
  - decisions made by people who won't give second thought a chance
  - actions made without a feeling of consequence.
  - The world before your eyes is the one, some might say is beyond repair.
  - A world doomed to fail.
  - 'And yet. Here you stand. '
  - 'Trying to make things right. Trying to fix this shithole. '
  - A world where things just stay.
  - Just the way they were left.
  - For someone to pickup. Just for a convenience.
  - Like a random shiny peeble on a road.
  - A plant that hasn't been watered for god knows how many days just begging for
    some rain.
  - Just trying to survive, trying to be itself.
  - But there is no rain coming.
  - 'All that is left is just waiting for the time to come. '
  - All the hope you may have had is lost.
